Package org.hibernate.cache.internal

Class EnabledCaching

java.lang.Object
org.hibernate.cache.internal.EnabledCaching
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cache, Serializable, Cache, DomainDataRegionBuildingContext, CacheImplementor, Service
public class EnabledCaching extends Object implements CacheImplementor, DomainDataRegionBuildingContext
A CacheImplementor service used when the second-level cache is enabled.
